{"tid":133404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【金正男未死？】死者肚腩冇紋身 日媒：可能係替身","createTime":"2017-02-24T14:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T04:32:22.000Z","uid":22736,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b4f68b75a04725f8fba010c17d3b434ba18ad971","tid":133404,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170224&amp;guid=56349072&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170224%26guid%3D56349072%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=8fb9f77e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170224%26guid%3D56349072%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=9df0dd0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170224&amp;guid=56349072&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n北韓領導人金正恩哥哥金正男上周一在馬來西亞被殺，驗屍初步結果顯示，在金正男臉上和眼上驗出VX神經毒劑。但有日本傳媒報道，由於死者身上沒有紋身，懷疑他並非金正男。<br />\n<br />\n日本富士電視台公開一張金正男於2013年拍攝的照片，他在照片中赤裸上身，樣貌與日前曝光的死者照片相似，只是多了鬍子，但富士電視台發放的照片中，男子的手臂和腹部都有紋身，和死者不同。報道事件的富士電視台女記者藤田水美表示，她和金正男曾見面、採訪和吃飯，次數不下30次，而紋身照片正正是金正男傳給她。<br />\n<br />\n而日本新聞網站「brandnew-s」的報道指，對金正男遭暗殺後的照片表示懷疑，認為死者可能根本不是金正男。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/24/224108_b05e991d96c7ba6749431c47585da9b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F24%2F224108_b05e991d96c7ba6749431c47585da9b0.jpg&h=178f2595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0753d3498faf26f8157c9b35ea34eea8d9190ad","tid":133404,"uid":42550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\